<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>When the UK leaves the EU there may be changes that affect your business. This leaflet contains some of the actions you can take now to help you prepare.</p>

<p>It also includes guidance on the wide range of support available to help your business grow as the UK leaves the EU.</p>

<p>This information is available to download for print or for viewing on screen.</p>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/business-uk-leaving-eu">Answer a few simple questions to find out how to prepare your business for EU Exit</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

